did.unittitle: Silliman College, Yale University, student records of the Classes of 1964-present maintained by the dean

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records consist of student records maintained by the dean of Silliman College, Yale University.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 13-L-1 (YRG 13-L-1), Records of the dean of Silliman College.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Records were transferred from the dean of Silliman College, 1975-2018.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the materials is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Silliman College, Yale University, Student Records of the Classes of 1964-present Maintained by the Dean (RU 257). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of student records maintained by the dean of Silliman College, Yale University.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.
